<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Your First Sale is Around the Corner! 🚀</title>
  <style>
    .head-con {
      width: 100%;
      height: 40px;
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    section {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
    }
    ul {
      text-align: left;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    li {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: green;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    a:hover {
      background-color: darkgreen;
    }
    .coupon {
      background-color: #e0ffe0;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border: 2px dashed green;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #2e7d32;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="head-con">
      <h2 class="head">Thriftify</h2>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>

    <div class="coupon">
      Use Coupon Code: <strong>THRIFTIFFY3000</strong> to give your customers ₦3,000 off their purchase!
    </div>

    <p>Simply share this code with potential buyers to encourage them to complete their purchase faster. 🚀</p>

    <p><strong>New Feature Alert! 💬</strong></p>
    <p>We’ve added a new <strong>chat feature</strong> so buyers can message you directly when interested in your item. 🛍️</p>
    <p><strong>Please try to appear online</strong> as much as possible — it builds trust and helps buyers get quick answers, which can increase your chances of making a sale!</p>

    <p>In addition, here are some tips to boost your chances of selling:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>✅ <strong>Use Clear & Attractive Photos</strong> – Well-lit, high-quality images get more attention.</li>
      <li>✅ <strong>Set Competitive Prices</strong> – Check similar listings and price your items to attract buyers.</li>
      <li>✅ <strong>Write a Detailed Description</strong> – Be honest about the condition, size, and features.</li>
      <li>✅ <strong>Share Your Listings</strong> – Promote your items on social media and WhatsApp groups.</li>
      <li>✅ <strong>Be Responsive</strong> – Buyers may have questions, so reply quickly to close the deal.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Your next buyer might already be looking for what you're selling! Stay patient, keep listing, and watch your sales grow. 🌟</p>

    <p>
      👉 <a href="{{link}}" target="_blank">View My Listings</a>
    </p>

    <p>If you need any help, feel free to reach out!</p>

    <p><b>Best regards,</b><br>The Thriftify Team</p>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
